#: ../../language/error_codes/E4174.md:1
msgid "E4174"
msgstr "E4174"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4174.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `control_in_defer`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`control_in_defer`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4174.md:5
msgid "Invalid control flow inside `defer`."
msgstr "`defer` 内部存在无效的控制流。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4174.md:7
msgid ""
"The right-hand side of `defer` is cleanup code that runs when the "
"surrounding scope exits. It cannot change how that surrounding scope "
"exits. MoonBit rejects `return`, `break`, `continue`, `raise`, calls to "
"functions that may raise, and async calls inside `defer`."
msgstr ""
"`defer` 右侧是清理代码，会在外围作用域退出时运行。它不能改变外围作用域的退出"
"方式。MoonBit 会拒绝 `defer` 内部的 `return`、`break`、`continue`、`raise`、对"
"可能抛出错误的函数的调用，以及 async 调用。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4174.md:12
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4174.md:14
msgid ""
"fn answer() -> Int {\n"
"  defer { return 42 }\n"
"  0\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4174.md:18
msgid ""
"The `return` would try to exit the surrounding function from cleanup "
"code, so it is rejected."
msgstr "`return` 会试图从清理代码中退出外围函数，因此会被拒绝。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4174.md:21
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4174.md:23
msgid ""
"Keep `defer` for cleanup with `Unit`-returning, non-raising, synchronous "
"code. Perform control flow after the deferred cleanup has been "
"registered."
msgstr ""
"只在返回 `Unit`、不会抛出错误的同步清理代码中使用 `defer`。控制流应在注册延迟"
"清理之后执行。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4174.md:26
msgid ""
"fn answer() -> Int {\n"
"  defer println(\"leaving answer\")\n"
"  42\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
